abstract: "ReliefGrid is an enterprise-grade autonomous multi-agent disaster coordination platform combining CockroachDB distributed transactional vector memory (pgvector), AWS Bedrock Claude 3 foundation agents, and OpenStreetMap/OSRM GIS pathfinding to dynamically resolve catastrophic crisis events."
